data.description: *** Seller is replacing the Carpets Downstairs and painting the walls downstairs to make this home even more MOVE-IN READY*****  Welcome to your dream home at 105 Gadwall Drive in the charming Stone Briar Subdivision of Easley, South Carolina! This beautiful residence offers the perfect blend of space, comfort, and convenience.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-designed 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home that's sure to check off all the boxes on your wish list. With a generous 2,476 square feet of living space, this home provides ample room for you and your family to spread out and make lasting memories.    The main level boasts a thoughtfully laid-out floor plan, featuring a bonus room that can serve as a versatile space for an office, playroom, or guest room. Additionally, a convenient half bathroom is located on this level for your guests' ease.    Upstairs, you'll discover all four bedrooms, providing a peaceful retreat for everyone in the family. The large laundry room on the upper floor adds to the practicality of this home, making chores a breeze.    For those who love to entertain or simply enjoy family meals together, you'll appreciate the presence of both a breakfast room and a formal dining room. The possibilities for hosting gatherings and creating cherished moments are endless.    One of the standout features of this home is its prime location within the highly sought-after Wren School District.     In addition to its fantastic features, this home offers the best of both worlds by being just a short 20-minute drive from the vibrant city of Greenville, SC. Enjoy easy access to all the amenities, dining, and entertainment that Greenville has to offer, while still relishing the tranquility of suburban living in Easley.   HVAC Units= 2019 and are under warranty  Septic Pumped and inspected= 12/8/23  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make 105 Gadwall Drive your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience firsthand the comfort and convenience that this lovely property has to offer.
